Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  都说不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咯吱咯吱  咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停手  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是小一的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把它落在游泳池边了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢谢你哦  我去交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是渚同学的…姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
