Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异母姐妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在同一天出生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不为人所知的秘密姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再追问了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过刚刚的话要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小一承受着巨大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对绝对要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会对任何人说起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渚同学大概也是这种感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕天女目呢  总感觉你很自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？我很自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说  总觉得你这样很棒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迟到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭是要吃速成咖喱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑛她很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开朗  又平易近人  真羡慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她能那么坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹  饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是夏祭的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你迷路的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是悠送给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是母亲的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  已经要出门了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥  今天轮到我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  悠  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是来得好早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为要换花儿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是悠你来得好早呀  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了  我有些事想单独和天女目谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…以前见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠你果然还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我真的超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是  能想起来真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏祭的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我们一起去捉知了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说  要抓一只珍奇的知了送给我  然后爬上了树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  连这都被你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这都是多早的事情了  别介意别介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  除此以外再没有母亲别的遗物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说我连母亲的记忆都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧  别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找吧  去找你母亲的挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这个星期天…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以倒是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就说定了  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身打扮是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事关个人隐私所以我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  和亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是星期天的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你浑身充满干劲呢  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是天女目  你这身打扮没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在这前面的杉树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面  就是我们捉知了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果弄丢了  就是丢在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我没事先告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候爬的树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被三年前的水土流失给冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目你在那儿等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换个地方看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要为我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说不用做到这种地步的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄丢挂坠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然马上露出笑脸对我说  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当你一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你的表情变得很忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\q2}而最近的那个早晨  我在教室又看到你和那时一样忧伤的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实一直都藏着忧伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我想让天女目能够一直露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  悠  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  天女目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  我会尽快洗好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服也没那么快烘干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把浴巾放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没听见了  有人进来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去都是爷爷先泡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再「呀呵」一下走进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得很让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先洗吧  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到脸的话会难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去经常像这样坐在爷爷的膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像碰到很硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问什么  就像这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是在做坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是悠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉依姬大人  我做了遭报应的事真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说不定还在世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一带的孩子全都由我奶奶负责过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会留下什么记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你的母亲可能也很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人太多  头都要晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找个地方休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等下不是要上台跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上场的时候就会认真加油的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供奉用的各种物品都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  准备齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去准备跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉依姬是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是供奉在这里的神灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我还是懂的  我不是问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉依姬是一位喜欢过几名人类的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人们却无法接受叉依姬的神圣与庄严
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果都离她而去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉依姬把这份悲伤藏在笑容背后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终决定一直默默地为人类的幸福祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌这样的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.97,incn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:10.64,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)}想屡战屡胜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦  初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有立直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还有三宝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  算上里宝一共七宝牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八寻姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会来拯救我吗  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话啊初佳  那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是犯花痴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我通过这场对局来占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能超过零分  那他对我也有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还能胜出的话  就能和他顺利交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在这里胡出起死回生的役满…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该打哪张好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吧  瑛  怎么想都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人确定？不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是老公确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这种玩法吗  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为游戏里没有这个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是执着的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  那里  不能挤…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  自摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:55.87,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}国破山河在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:55.87,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,你也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.46,0:25:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的笑容背后所封闭的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.91,0:25:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算能被明亮地照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.21,0:25:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定会伤害到他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.33,0:25:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  悠  这样子就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.39,0:25:43.94,next,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,280)}瑛不言弃
